summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and West Sixty-fifth Street from Greenwood Avenue to Eighth Avenue Northwest et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 20424, creating Local Improvement District No. 2019 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
